:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/23/151725_2ddc26651206183c3926b7fa05bfdf70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F23%2F151725_2ddc26651206183c3926b7fa05bfdf70.png&h=63ddaaa8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b6f18c7e3a905953ab511301bf3106134422df2","tid":635652,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad2ca3f78ddc39cfe3e26f2f3077dc8163eae34b","tid":635652,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37a2f28054c7a9f98b1e8ce84c81fe2b06804929","tid":635652,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37cbbc1f46b3c429853309258dce67bd195a09d7","tid":635652,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T09:36:04.000Z","msg":"下季邊個教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/23/122235_f78492f0513c659e69dab2e47f567202.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F23%2F122235_f78492f0513c659e69dab2e47f567202.gif&h=0c02ec15&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/23/151725_2ddc26651206183c3926b7fa05bfdf70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F23%2F151725_2ddc26651206183c3926b7fa05bfdf70.png&h=63ddaaa8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英國傳媒報導，愛美麗兩週前的面試交流中，用令人信服的表現征服了阿仙奴的招聘小隊。<br />\n<br />\n由加薛迪斯、辛列希和米斯連達組成的阿仙奴面試團隊，對一眾領隊候選人進行了面試。愛美麗在面試過程中，科學地分析了阿仙奴每一個球員，並且提供了詳細的數據統計和改進方案。<br />\n<br />\n愛美麗明確地表示，他要圍繞著艾朗藍斯及奧巴美揚建隊，而且他對球隊的了解程度亦讓加薛迪斯的團隊折服震驚，同時讓其他候選人黯然失色，包括呼聲頗高的阿迪達。<br />\n<br />\n愛美麗和哥迪奧拿一樣注意細節，而他的激情演說亦征服了加薛迪斯。他比在球會工作多年的人更了解阿仙奴的團隊，包括每一個球員的職業發展及傷患歷史。<br />\n<br />\n而且，愛美麗從一開始就表態，他會接受阿仙奴財務狀況的改變，並習慣於在類似的工作架構中工作。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf8975eb9360f9ddaf2a4dd43c3206fa4eab240","tid":635652,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T08:43:04.000Z","msg":"官宣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3cbc6a62620b7153444e3d04cce42ab84cb9bb","tid":635652,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:30:13.000Z","msg":"雲加會唔會去教皇馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22baf57dfbe071fb56aca6cc93dd6b34d9aad1b8","tid":635652,"uid":18912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:58:51.000Z","msg":"想睇雲家馬德里<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}